				You give the gnoll teeth to the only woman in the warrior pit, in Halas. This will increase your faction with the Steel Warriors of Halas.<BR>
<BR>
Which brings me to my question. There is a question you can ask Renth to determine your faction status. I am uncertain as to the exact phrasing. It is something like, &quot;What about this dangerous buisness.&quot;<BR>
<BR>
If he tells you about the murders, you have the faction. If not he tells you to hook up with the gal in the warrior pit to do the gnoll teeth quest.<BR>
<BR>
If anyone knows the exact phrasing of the question, a post here would be nice.<BR>
